hopobject.body: Go travelling natural synergy day spa facebook Having recently attended a play in Surrey at a place called Wintershall, I saw a pair of well looked after Camels as part of the cast of the play. I do like the idea of the ban on animals being USED in circuses but however, there are cases such as the above stated where the animals are well looked after and loved. Yes and what about semi-domesticated wild animals, fancy a pet racoon or grey parrot
